OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,7,Fbubbling up over inland areas by
OL,8,Fafternoon. Warm inland and in the
OL,9,Fwest, a little cooler near east coast
OL,10,Fbut the best of the sunshine there.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine warm sunny evening
OL,13,Fwith remaining cloud breaking up. Some
OL,14,Fclear spells at first tonight but
OL,15,Fclouding over, perhaps the odd light
OL,16,Fshower.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FIt will be a cloudier day,
OL,19,Fperhaps with the odd shower, but it
OL,20,Fshould brighten up later in the day
OL,21,Fwith some warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
